                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The U.S.-China joint announcement on climate change is an historic milestone to limit carbon pollution. This agreement between the world‚Äôs two top economies, which together emit nearly 45 percent of the planet‚Äôs carbon pollution<sup><a href="united-states-china-cooperation?quicktabs_1=0#fn1" id="ref1">1</a></sup>, is a big deal.</p></div>
