                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/china-agrees-end-wind-power-subsidies-wto-consultations">China Agrees to End Wind Power Subsidies in WTO Consultations</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/windturbineinstall.jpg" alt="" title="" width="160" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
