  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>On January 18, at a ceremony at the <a href="http://www.brookings.edu/events/2009/1021_china_clean_energy.aspx">US-China Strategic Forum on Clean Energy Cooperation</a> in Washington, D.C., U.S. Department of Energy Secretary Steven Chu and China‚Äôs Energy Minister Zhang Guogao and Science and Technology Minister Wan Gang signed an agreement to <a href="http://www.wri.org/press/2011/01/us-and-china-sign-agreement-advance-clean-energy-research-center-cerc">advance</a> the <a href="http://www.us-chinacerc.org/index.html">US-China Clean Energy Research Center</a> (CERC).</p></div>
