  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Banning Garrett is a Washington-based strategic thinker, writer, convener, and entrepreneur. He works at the intersection of policy, technology, long-term global trends, urbanization, and geopolitics. Garrett also has made presentations to think tanks, business groups, international conferences, and governments in Asia, Africa, Latin America, Europe and the United States, and has written for more than two dozen journals and media outlets.</p></div>
